Package picscout.depend.dependency.interfaces

Interfaces for all classes, used for abstraction of implementation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMapBuilder
    Builder of dependency maps.
    IProject
    Project has a descriptor, and ability to calculate dependent projects based on its csproj file.
    IProjectBuilder
    Construct a project from a path
    IProjectDependencyMapper
    Maps projects dependencies
    IProjectDescriptor
    Descriptor for a project
    IProjectStore
    Holds all projects mapped to guid and assembly name
    ISolution
    Solution as defined in .sln file
    ISolutionBuilder
    Builds a solution.
    ISolutionMapper
    Map dependencies between solutions
    IStatePersist
    Persist or load persisted state
